text: Volosyanka () is an inhabited locality in Ukraine and it may refer to: * Volosyanka, Skole Raion, a village in Skole Raion, Lviv Oblast * Volosyanka, Velykyi Bereznyi Raion, a village in Velykyi Bereznyi Raion, Zakarpattia Oblast ==See also== * Mala Volosyanka, village in Turka Raion, Lviv Oblast
title: Volosyanka
